Cisco-IOS-XR-l2vpn-oper API API Reference

API generated from Cisco-IOS-XR-l2vpn-oper@2018-08-01.yang

API Endpoint
http://{Controller-IP}:{Controller-Port}/restconf/operational/network-topology:network-topology/topology/topology-netconf/node/{{router}}/yang-ext:mount/
URL '/' code: %2F
Schemes: http
Version: 1.0.0

in path

in path
